      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·谷風之什·007.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">小明.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>嗟爾君子，無恆安處。靖共爾位，正直是與。神之聽之，式穀以女。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Ah! ye gentlemen,
Do not reckon on your rest ​being permanent.
Quietly fulfil the duties of your offices,
Associating with the correct and upright;
So shall the spirits hearken to you,
And give you good.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
