      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·谷風之什·007.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">小明.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>嗟爾君子，無恆安息。靖共爾位，好是正直。神之聽之，介爾景福。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Ah! ye gentlemen,
Do not reckon on your repose being permanent.
Quietly fulfil the duties of your offices,
Loving the correct and upright;
So shall the spirits hearken to you,
And give you large measures of bright happiness.</seg>
      </tuv>
